ass=\\\"px-8 py-3 bg-white text-black font-bold rounded-xl text-sm hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors shadow-lg\\\">\\n          GENERATE SHORTS\\n        </button>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <!-- Right Column: Shorts Preview -->\\n    <div class=\\\"w-1/2 flex items-center justify-center\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"relative\\\">\\n        <!-- Glowing Aura for Phone -->\\n        <div class=\\\"absolute inset-0 bg-blue-500/30 blur-[60px] rounded-full scale-90\\\"></div>\\n        \\n        <!-- Mobile Frame -->\\n        <div class=\\\"w-[320px] h-[640px] bg-[#111] rounded-[3rem] border-[8px] border-[#222] shadow-2xl overflow-hidden relative\\\">\\n          <!-- Shorts Content Simulation -->\\n          <div class=\\\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#1a1a1a] to-[#000]\\\">\\n            <!-- Problem Content Overlay -->\\n            <div class=\\\"pt-12 px-6\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-lg mb-4\\\">\\n                <p class=\\\"text-black text-[10px] font-bold border-b border-black/10 pb-1 mb-2\\\">2024 CSAT MATHEMATICS Q30</p>\\n                <div class=\\\"text-black text-[12px] leading-tight font-serif\\\">\\n                  \355\225\250\354\210\230 f(x) = (x-1)e^x \354\227\220 \353\214\200\355\225\230\354\227\254...<br>\\n                  \353\260\251\354\240\225\354\213\235 |f(x) - k| = g(x)... \\n                </div>\\n              </div>\\n              \\n              <!-- Step by Step Animation Mock -->\\n              <div class=\\\"space-y-3\\\">\\n                <div class=\\\"p-3 bg-blue-900/40 border border-blue-400/30 rounded-xl backdrop-blur-sm\\\">\\n                  <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-blue-300 font-mono\\\">Step 01: Function Analysis</p>\\n                  <p class=\\\"text-xs\\\">f\'(x) = x e^x</p>\\n                </div>\\n                <div class=\\\"p-3 bg-purple-900/40 border border-purple-400/30 rounded-xl backdrop-blur-sm opacity-60\\\">\\n                  <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-purple-300 font-mono\\\">Step 02: Critical Points</p>\\n                  <p class=\\\"text-xs\\\">x = 0 (Inflection Point)</p>\\n                </div>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n\\n            <!-- Shorts UI Elements -->\\n            <div class=\\\"absolute bottom-8 left-4 right-4 flex items-end justify-between\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"flex-1\\\">\\n                <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\\\">\\n                  <div class=\\\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-500\\\"></div>\\n                  <p class=\\\"text-xs font-bold\\\">@MathShortsAI</p>\\n                  <button class=\\\"px-2 py-0.5 bg-red-600 rounded text-[9px] font-bold uppercase\\\">Follow</button>\\n                </div>\\n                <p class=\\\"text-[10px] leading-relaxed text-white/80\\\">\\n                  2024 \354\210\230\353\212\245 \354\210\230\355\225\231 30\353\262\210 \355\202\254\353\237\254\353\254\270\355\225\255 60\354\264\210 \355\222\200\354\235\264 \360\237\224\245 #\354\210\230\353\212\245 #\354\210\230\355\225\231 #\353\257\270\354\240\201\353\266\204\\n                </p>\\n              </div>\\n              <div class=\\\"flex flex-col gap-5 items-center pb-2\\\">\\n                <div class=\\\"flex flex-col items-center gap-1\\\"><div class=\\\"w-5 h-5 bg-white/20 rounded\\\"></div><span class=\\\"text-[8px]\\\">12.4k</span></div>\\n                <div class=\\\"flex flex-col items-center gap-1\\\"><div class=\\\"w-5 h-5 bg-white/20 rounded\\\"></div><span class=\\\"text-[8px]\\\">342</span></div>\\n                <div class=\\\"flex flex-col items-center gap-1\\\"><div class=\\\"w-5 h-5 bg-white/20 rounded\\\"></div><span class=\\\"text-[8px]\\\">Share</span></div>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n          \\n          <!-- Notch -->\\n          <div class=\\\"absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-32 h-6 bg-[#222] rounded-b-2xl\\\"></div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </main>\\n\\n  <!-- Bottom Status Bar -->\\n  <footer class=\\\"relative z-10 h-10 bg-black/40 border-t border-white/5 flex items-center px-8 justify-between text-[10px] text-white/30 uppercase tracking-widest\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex gap-6\\\">\\n      <span>Session: Active</span>\\n      <span>Cloud Sync: Enabled</span>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"flex gap-6\\\">\\n      <span>GPU Acceleration: 100%</span>\\n      <span>\302\251 2024 MATHSHORTS INC.</span>\\n    </div>\\n  </footer>\\n</div>\\n                    </body>\\n                  </html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
    items {
      text: "Apply the \"Immersive UI\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Immersive UI\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"w-[1024px] h-[768px] bg-[#050505] text-white font-sans flex flex-col overflow-hidden relative\\\">\\n  <!-- Atmospheric Background Glows -->\\n  <div class=\\\"absolute top-[-10%] left-[-10%] w-[40%] h-[40%] bg-blue-600/20 rounded-full blur-[120px]\\\"></div>\\n  <div class=\\\"absolute bottom-[-10%] right-[-10%] w-[40%] h-[40%] bg-purple-600/20 rounded-full blur-[120px]\\\"></div>\\n\\n  <!-- Header Navigation -->\\n  <nav class=\\\"relative z-10 flex items-center justify-between px-8 h-20 border-b border-white/10 backdrop-blur-md bg-black/20\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-purple-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/20\\\">\\n        <svg class=\\\"w-6 h-6 text-white\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M9 7h6m0 10v-3m-3 3h.01M9 17h.01M9 14h.01M12 14h.01M15 11h.01M12 11h.01M9 11h.01M7 21h10a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z\\\"></path></svg>\\n      </div>\\n      <div>\\n        <h1 class=\\\"text-xl font-bold tracking-tight\\\">MATH<span class=\\\"text-blue-400\\\">SHORTS</span> AI</h1>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-white/40 uppercase tracking-[0.2em]\\\">Suneung Solver Engine v2.0</p>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-6\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex gap-4 text-sm font-medium text-white/60\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-blue-400\\\">Generator</span>\\n        <span>Gallery</span>\\n        <span>Subscription</span>\\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/10 border border-white/20 flex items-center justify-center\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"w-2 h-2 bg-green-400 rounded-full animate-pulse\\\"></div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </nav>\\n\\n  <!-- Main Workspace -->\\n  <main class=\\\"relative z-10 flex flex-1 p-8 gap-8\\\">\\n    \\n    <!-- Left Column: Problem Input -->\\n    <div class=\\\"w-1/2 flex flex-col gap-6\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex-1 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-3xl p-8 backdrop-blur-xl relative group\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"absolute inset-0 border border-blue-500/20 rounded-3xl pointer-events-none\\\"></div>\\n        <div class=\\\"h-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center border-2 border-dashed border-white/10 rounded-2xl\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"w-16 h-16 bg-white/5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 border border-white/10\\\">\\n            <svg class=\\\"w-8 h-8 text-blue-400\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-8l-4-4m0 0L8 8m4-4v12\\\"></path></svg>\\n          </div>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-lg font-medium\\\">Upload Math Problem</p>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-sm text-white/40 mt-1\\\">Drag & drop image from Workbook (PDF, PNG, JPG)</p>\\n          <div class=\\\"mt-8 p-4 bg-black/40 rounded-xl border border-white/10 flex items-center gap-4\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-12 h-12 bg-white/5 rounded-lg overflow-hidden border border-white/10\\\">\\n               <div class=\\\"w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center text-[8px] opacity-40\\\">EBS_MATH.PNG</div>\\n            </div>\\n            <div>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-xs font-mono\\\">EBS_Level3_Calc_30.png</p>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-green-400 uppercase\\\">Ready to synthesize</p>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n      \\n      <div class=\\\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-700 rounded-2xl p-4 flex items-center justify-between shadow-2xl shadow-blue-600/20\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex flex-col\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-white/70\\\">Engine Status</span>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-sm font-medium\\\">Advanced Step-by-Step Logic v4</span>\\n        </div>\\n        <button class=\\\